news.title: Swedish Skanska reports rise in net profit by 1.8% in Q1 2024
news.para: The Nordic region's biggest construction group said operating earnings rose to 497 million crowns ($45.6 million) from a year-ago 394 million, lagging the 873 million seen in a LSEG compilation of analysts' forecasts.

news.title: Commercial property prices in Germany drop by 9.6% in Q1 2024
news.para: The continuing decline in values of commercial real estate follows a 10.2% drop for all of 2023. The latest data are less than the 12.1% drop for the fourth quarter, which was the biggest ever.

news.title: Peninsula Land, Delta Corp, AA Group to set up Rs 765 crore realty platform
news.para: This joint entity will undertake residential redevelopment in the Mumbai Metropolitan Region and plotted development in and around the Mumbai region, Alibaug, Khopoli, Karjat and Pune.

news.title: Human rights commission summons Maharashtra govt, Cidco in Belapur Hill land grab
news.para: Commission addresses Belapur Hill encroachments, warns of landslides. Chief Secretary to assign responsibility among Cidco, NMMC Commissioner, and Forest department to protect residents' rights.

news.title: Delhi HC asks authorities to state timeline to complete survey of land
news.para: Both the MCD and DDA are directed to finalise the agency from whom the survey of Delhi is to be conducted and provide a timeline when it will be completed," said a bench of Acting Chief Justice Manmohan and Justice Manmeet P S Arora.

news.title: Over 1,450 high-rises built without mandatory Nagpur civic body's nod: Audit
news.para: Data from the Nagpur Municipal Corporation (NMC) reveals that out of 7,054 buildings, having a height of over 15m height, 1,459 lack the mandatory no-objection certificates (NOC) from the fire department.

news.title: Bigbloc Construction's net profit up 55% in Q4 FY24
news.para: The company's revenue from operations soared by 46 per cent to Rs 67.95 crore in the last quarter of 2023-24 compared to Rs 46.55 crore in the last quarter of 2022-23.

news.title: Incuspaze leases 3.5 lakh sq ft office space in Gurugram
news.para: The company has also leased 150,000 sq ft space in Pune and 60,000 sq ft space in Jaipur, as it is looking to add 1.5 million sq ft this year owing to increasing demand for flexible space in the country.

news.title: Ghost shopping malls space up 58% in 2023 across eight cities: Report
news.para: As many as 64 shopping malls with about 13.3 million square feet of gross leasable area have been categorised as 'Ghost Shopping Centre' in 2023.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC releases list of 188 dangerous, dilapidated buildings
news.para: Of the 188 buildings on the list, the highest 114 structures are in the western suburbs, followed by the eastern suburbs with 47 and 27 in the island city, the release said.

news.title: Delhi civic body's desilting plan to cover all illegal colonies
news.para: MCD aims to clear away 1,27,608 tonnes of waste from 713 drains that are more than 4ft deep and 82,642 tonnes from 20,884 smaller drains.

news.title: Suraj Estate Developers' net profit up 17.44% quarter-on-quarter in Q4 FY24
news.para: Suraj Estate Developers' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 103.03 crore in Q4 FY24, a drop of 2.93 per cent from Rs 106.14 crore it recorded in Q3 FY24.

news.title: Kamdhenu Ventures posts net profit of Rs 4.19 crore in Q4 FY24
news.para: Kamdhenu Ventures net consolidated total income stood at Rs 85.29 crore in Q4 FY24, a growth of 21.34 per cent from Rs 70.29 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Simon Property Group posts revenue of $1.44 billion in Q1 2024
news.para: Simon Property expects FFO per share to be in the range of $12.75 to $12.90, compared with its prior FFO forecast of $11.85 to $12.10 per share.

news.title: House prices in UK rise by 0.1% in April 2024: Halifax
news.para: Tuesday's data marks a return to monthly growth after prices fell 0.9% in March - the first decline since September and comes after rival mortgage lender Nationwide reported an unexpected 0.4% April price drop last week.

news.title: Redfin agrees to pay $9.25 million to settle real estate broker commission lawsuits
news.para: The online brokerage and real estate services company disclosed the proposed settlement Monday in a regulatory filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission.

news.title: Bajaj Housing Finance raises Rs 4,500 crore through bonds
news.para: Market sources said that Bajaj Housing Finance has raised Rs 4,500 crore through two issuances of non-convertible debentures – Rs 3,000 crore through a 3-year bond at an interest rate of 8.10% and Rs 1,500 crore through a 5-year bond at 8.05%.

news.title: Geberit posts EBITDA of 274.9 million francs in Q1 2024
news.para: Geberit reported sales of 837.2 million Swiss francs ($923.25 million) for the quarter, down 6.2% on the same time last year, but beating the consensus estimate of 832 million Swiss francs in an analyst poll conducted by newswire AWP.

news.title: SC orders ED to not harass district collectors in Tamil Nadu over Illegal sand mining
news.para: During the hearing on Monday, senior advocate Kapil Sibal, appearing for the state, told a bench of Justices Bela M Trivedi and Pankaj Mithal that the district collectors had appeared before the ED.
